9. Practical Advice for the LCC President Using Copilot
As you use these prompts, think like a product owner, not just a builder.
Ask after each Copilot pass:
Does this make the club more effective?
Can I maintain this in real life?
Will another person understand it later?
Is this feature actually necessary now?
Are we building trust or just adding software?
That mindset will protect the project more than any framework choice.
